## Done — DRS-27 Complete

**18/18 tests passing**, no type errors in our files.

### What was built:

1. **`src/components/responsive/detail-view.tsx`** — New reusable `DetailView` component with mobile/tablet/desktop breakpoint handling via `useResponsiveNav`. Mobile shows one panel at a time with back button; tablet/desktop shows side-by-side grid split.

2. **`src/app/(app)/events/[eventId]/sessions/sessions-manager-client.tsx`** — Migrated to use `DetailView`:
   - **Desktop**: Table layout with Title/Hall/Time/Type/Status columns. Click row → detail panel opens on right showing full session info + Edit link.
   - **Mobile**: Card layout preserved. Tap card → navigates to session detail page.
   - **Fluid typography**: `text-fluid-lg` / `text-fluid-sm` on headings and text.
   - **New detail panel**: Shows session type, title, description, hall, time, speakers, role requirements, CME credits, and sub-sessions.

3. **Test files**: 7 DetailView tests + 11 session manager responsive tests.

